Suggestion: Preserve Leading Whitespace
One possible fix is to modify the function to preserve the leading whitespace when wrapping the text. This can be done by using the `substring` method to extract the leading whitespace from the text and then appending it to the StringBuffer. Here is an example of how this could be implemented:
```java
